FAQs
Why should I study in Canada?

Studying in Canada offers high-quality education, affordable tuition fees, a multicultural environment, excellent work opportunities, and a safe and welcoming society.

How can Qadri-International help with my study in Canada?

Qadri-International provides personalized counseling, university selection assistance, comprehensive application support, and visa and immigration guidance.

What are some top universities in Canada?

Some of the top universities in Canada include the University of Toronto, McGill University, and the University of British Columbia.

Are there work opportunities for international students in Canada?

Yes, international students can work part-time during the academic year and full-time during scheduled breaks. The Post-Graduation Work Permit (PGWP) program also allows graduates to gain valuable work experience.

How do I choose the right university for my studies?

Qadri-International helps you choose the right university by considering your academic profile, career goals, and personal preferences.
